NameAlreadyExists=You already have an API key with this name. Please use a different name or delete the existing key.\nOr use /cancel if you want to cancel the current operation.
AlreadyExists=You already saved the given API key. Please try a different one or use /cancel to cancel the operation.
NotPremium=The SauceNAO account to which this API key belongs is using a free tier. Unfortunately, free accounts are ratelimited by IP, so, you'll need an enhanced account to save this API key.\nPlease try again with a different one or use /cancel to cancel the operation.
InvalidKey=The given API key is invalid. Please try a different one or use /cancel to cancel the operation.
SearchLimitReached=Ups, the api key validation failed due rate limits. Please wait a moment and try again.\nOr use /cancel to cancel the operation.
CannotValidateKey=Cannot validate the given API key right now. Try again later.
UnknownError=An unknown error occurred while saving your apikey. Try again later.
